OL,3,CIran insists it will 'proudly'
OL,4,Cparticipate in World Cup despite war
OL,5,Cwith US
OL,7,FIran is preparing for a "proud and
OL,8,Fsuccessful participation" in this
OL,9,Fsummer's World Cup, a government
OL,10,Fspokesperson has said.
OL,12,FIt has been unclear whether the
OL,13,FIranian team would travel to the
OL,14,Ftournament, hosted by the US, Canada
OL,15,Fand Mexico this summer, since joint
OL,16,FAmerican and Israeli strikes in
OL,17,FFebruary.
OL,19,FBut ITV News has learnt that US entry
OL,20,Fvisas for the Iranian national team
OL,21,Fare already being processed.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
