PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776996209
OL,3,CIran insists it will 'proudly'
OL,4,Cparticipate in World Cup despite war
OL,5,Cwith US
OL,7,FPresident Trump previously said the
OL,8,Fsquad would be welcome but suggested
OL,9,Fplaying in the US may not be
OL,10,Fappropriate "for their own life and
OL,11,Fsafety."
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, a Trump envoy told The
OL,14,FFinancial Times he had asked the US
OL,15,Fpresident and FIFA to replace Iran
OL,16,Fwith Italy, which failed to qualify
OL,17,Ffor the World Cup for the third time
OL,18,Fin a row.
OL,26,@rD@MOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776996209
OL,3,CIran insists it will 'proudly'
OL,4,Cparticipate in World Cup despite war
OL,5,Cwith US
OL,7,FThe newspaper reports that the idea
OL,8,Fwas an attempt to repair the
OL,9,Frelationship between the president and
OL,10,FItalian Prime Minister Giorgia Meloni
OL,11,Fafter the pair fell out last week over
OL,12,FTrump's remarks about Pope Leo XIV.
OL,14,FUS special envoy Paolo Zampolli also
OL,15,Ftold CNN he suggested the plan to
OL,16,FTrump and FIFA president Gianni
OL,17,FInfantino, adding that it was his
OL,18,Funderstanding that Iran was not
OL,19,Fplanning to participate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776996209
OL,3,CIran insists it will 'proudly'
OL,4,Cparticipate in World Cup despite war
OL,5,Cwith US
OL,7,F"A World Cup without Messi is not a
OL,8,FWorld Cup," he said. "Italy has the
OL,9,Fsame merits after winning four times
OL,10,Fthe World Cup."
OL,12,FFIFA declined to comment on record
OL,13,Fabout Zampolli's remarks, but referred
OL,14,FITV News to remarks by FIFA president
OL,15,FGianni Infantino just last week.
OL,17,F"The Iranian team is coming for sure,"
OL,18,Fhe said. "Yes. Yes. We hope, we hope
OL,19,Fthat by then, of course, the situation
OL,20,Fwill be a peaceful situation."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@KO]pD@VOUrD@OO]zD@JOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
