PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776996209
OL,3,CIran insists it will 'proudly'
OL,4,Cparticipate in World Cup despite war
OL,5,Cwith US
OL,7,FItaly failed to qualify after losing
OL,8,Fto world No. 65 Bosnia and Herzegovina
OL,9,Fin the playoff final, and despite the
OL,10,Fnation's rich football history, it is
OL,11,Funlikely to accept Washington's olive
OL,12,Fbranch.
OL,14,F"It's not appropriate, you qualify on
OL,15,Fthe pitch," was the opinion of Italy's
OL,16,Fminister of sport, Andrea Abodi,
OL,17,Faccording to ANSA, the national news
OL,18,Fagency.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@KO]
