OL,3,CIran insists it will 'proudly'
OL,4,Cparticipate in World Cup despite war
OL,5,Cwith US
OL,7,FMeanwhile, a government spokesperson
OL,8,Ftold Iranian state TV on Wednesday
OL,9,Fthat "the Ministry of Youth and Sports
OL,10,Fmade an announcement about the full
OL,11,Fpreparedness of our national soccer
OL,12,Fteam for presence in the 2026 World
OL,13,FCup in the US, by the order of the
OL,14,Fminister."
OL,16,FSpokesperson Fatemeh Mohejerani added
OL,17,Fthat "the necessary arrangements that
OL,18,Fthese dear ones need for the team's
OL,19,Fproud and successful participation,
OL,20,F(have been made)".
OL,26,@qD@FOUvD@JO]yD@FOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
