OL,3,CIran insists it will 'proudly'
OL,4,Cparticipate in World Cup despite war
OL,5,Cwith US
OL,7,FIran is set to play New Zealand, Egypt
OL,8,Fand Belgium this summer, with two
OL,9,Fmatches being hosted in Los Angeles
OL,10,Fand the other in Seattle.
OL,12,FIf both the US and Iran finish second
OL,13,Fin their respective groups, they would
OL,14,Fthen play each other in the round of
OL,15,F32 in Dallas on July 3.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
