OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776996209
OL,3,CIran insists it will 'proudly'
OL,4,Cparticipate in World Cup despite war
OL,5,Cwith US
OL,7,FLast month, Iranian soccer president
OL,8,FMehdi Taj said the nation's federation
OL,9,Fwas in discussions with FIFA about
OL,10,Fmoving its World Cup matches from the
OL,11,FUS to Mexico, which is co-hosting the
OL,12,Ftournament along with Canada. It
OL,13,Ffollowed President Trump's suggestion
OL,14,Fthat Iran's players and staff may not
OL,15,Fbe safe in the United States.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
