CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776996209
OL,3,CIran insists it will 'proudly'
OL,4,Cparticipate in World Cup despite war
OL,5,Cwith US
OL,7,FFIFA president Infantino is also
OL,8,Fconfident that Iran will play as
OL,9,Fplanned, saying last week that they
OL,10,Fwould "for sure".
OL,12,F"We hope that by then, of course, the
OL,13,Fsituation will be a peaceful
OL,14,Fsituation. As I said, that would
OL,15,Fdefinitely help," he said at CNBC's
OL,16,FInvest in America Forum.
OL,18,F"But Iran has to come. Of course, they
OL,19,Frepresent their people. They have
OL,20,Fqualified. The players want to play."
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@PO]tD@AOUwD@QO]zD@AOU|D@eO]
