OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776996209
OL,3,CIran insists it will 'proudly'
OL,4,Cparticipate in World Cup despite war
OL,5,Cwith US
OL,7,FInfantino promised the Iranian team
OL,8,Fthree weeks ago that he would help
OL,9,Ffind a training camp outside of the
OL,10,Fcountry for the team to prepare for
OL,11,Fthe World Cup.
OL,13,FThat could also be in Turkey, where
OL,14,FIran played warm-up games last month
OL,15,Fin Antalya against Nigeria and Costa
OL,16,FRica.
OL,18,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,19,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,20,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,21,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
